gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 114, Lakers 106
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets ended the game on a 10-2 run as they defeated the Lakers, 114-106. Jamal Murray led the way for the Nuggets with 29 points (5-9 3pt. FG), seven rebounds and 11 assists, while Nikola Jokic added 24 points, 13 rebounds and nine assists in the victory. Anthony Davis (32 points, nine rebounds) and LeBron James (25 points, nine rebounds, seven assists) combined for 57 points for the Lakers in the losing effort. The Nuggets win their third straight game as they improve to 36-16 on the season, while the Lakers fall to 27-26.
